column2: "A new stream may eventually form a tributary. This may be one of those times."
"Multiple streams are starting to converge towards a single end."
"Should that result be called a tragedy is a matter for individuals to decide."
"We know that. And that is why we are unable to say anything."
"Knowing and deciding are only two illusions, what's required is experience."
"All I and We can do is guide you, and provide insight."
"To follow or not to follow is a matter for you to decide on your own."
"A final result is approaching, as long as you experience that we are satisfied."
